# Commit message format: <type>(<scope>): <subject>
#
# Types: feat, fix, docs, style, refactor, perf, test, chore, ci, revert, security
#
# Examples:
#   feat(api): add wallet transaction history endpoint
#   fix(conductor): handle timeout during execution
#   docs: update API reference with new endpoints
#   refactor(wallet): simplify balance check logic
#   test(api): add unit tests for selection algorithm
#   ci: add CodeQL security scanning workflow
#   chore(deps): upgrade framer-motion to v11
#   security: add input validation to auth routes